-- NextEra Energy Sells Hydro Assets in Maine and New Hampshire
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K e l e m e n
-- 2012-12-22T00:35:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-22/nextera-energy-sells-hydro-assets-in-maine-and-new-hampshire.html
NextEra Energy Resources LLC, a
subsidiary of  NextEra Energy Inc (NEE) , agreed to sell hydro-
generation assets in  New Hampshire  and  Maine  to a unit of
Brookfield Renewable Energy Partners.  The sale is based on an enterprise value of about $760
million and includes $700 million of non-recourse debt, NextEra
said in a statement today. The deal’s price wasn’t disclosed.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jasmina Kelemen at 
 jkelemen2@bloomberg.net  